snippet.title: Is it splitsville for Amber Heard, her boyfriend Elon Musk? - Hollywood News
snippet.description:
--------------------------------------
New Delhi, Aug 07 (ANI): If sources are to be believed, then, American actress Amber Heard and her boyfriend Tesla CEO Elon Musk have called it quits after a year-long romance. As per a report in Us Magazine, the billionaire tech mogul and his actress girlfriend's busy schedule resulted in the breakup.
